<section class="na-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="na-series mono">🔬 PROJECT · ARCHIVE MIGRATION</div>
    <h1 class="na-title">Photo Archive Migration<br/><span style="font-size:0.6em;color:var(--teal)">PastPerfect 5 → NPGallery</span></h1>
    <div class="na-meta mono">Dan Sullivan with the NEST AI Crew · methodology visible at <a href="/journal" style="color:var(--teal)">/journal</a></div>
    <p class="na-deck">A migration that preserves the catalog as a catalog, not a spreadsheet of filenames. Three layers travel intact across the stack-translation. The architecture was named in <a href="/journal/003" style="color:var(--teal)"><strong>NOW ANTHROPOLOGY 003</strong></a> ("Three-Layer Archive: Pokémon, PastPerfect, and the Waywoodarium Save State"). This page is the shape of the work that runs on top of it.</p>
